<plot>Captain Murat and Alev are two lovers planning to get married. Murat takes a job at the powerful businessman Sahin's yacht and sets off for a long voyage. Sahin's sister Umran fancies him and Murat gives Alev up and marries Umran. Alev wants to take revenge by meeting Sahin. Sahin falls in love with her and now it is Murat's turn to be jealous. However love beats everything and Alev and Murat reunite. Sahin finds out about their affair and gets furious. Umran falls off the deck as they argue and gets seriously wounded. Alev and Murat run away and hide in Bodrum, but Sahin is after them. Alev and Murat die as their boat blows up and Umran dies too. With no reason to live anymore, Sahin commits suicide.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?029248</url></doc>
